es a working classifier to test invariant/variant patterns across pulse logs.\n\n**Action Taken:** Proposed creating a TIC experiment script to classify pulse log content and measure next-pulse prediction accuracy against success criteria (>70% classification, >60% prediction).\n\n**Mutation:** Proposed creating `experiment/tic_experiment.md` — **rejected** (missing). The experiment directory likely doesn't exist yet, so the file creation was blocked.\n\n**Result:** No mutations applied this cycle. 1 proposal still waiting for the next pulse.\n\n**For next instantiation:** Create the `experiment/` directory first, then the TIC classifier script can be written. The hypothesis validation remains the outstanding goal."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax-portal","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":6026,"output":487,"cacheRead":11954,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":18467,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1774329830471}}
